 <li class="flex items-start"><span class="text-green-500 mr-2">-</span>You prefer gamified, bite-sized lessons</li>
 <li class="flex items-start"><span class="text-green-500 mr-2">-</span>You want to supplement live tutoring with daily practice</li>
 </ul>
